18.6.2 ecm3_dtsyscom__SendMuData
� General Information
This module transmits the information data to the MU using dedicated BSW interfaces.
Transmitted data are only sent to Monitoring Unit using ACTION_INFR_ECM3Set*, but not evaluated.
Output transmit command is updated according to STATE_MC.
The communication is triggered by the MC by calling ACTION_INFR_ECM3TriggerComMcMu() once the data
have been sent to the infrastructure by the responsible command.
